Swifter Privacy Policy
At Wido, one of our main priorities is the privacy our users. Here is a Privacy Policy to explain our practices regarding the collection and use of information within the app Swifter.
​
Within the app Swifter, we might offer you the possibility (which is not an obligation in any case) to provide us with your email address. We may use your email address to contact you with newsletters, marketing or promotional materials and other information that may be interest to you. You may opt out of receiving any, or all, of these communications from us by following the unsubscribe link or instructions provided in any email we send.
​
Swifter does not collect any other personal information at all.
​
REVISIONS TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY
​
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. You are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. These changes are effective immediately upon posting this page.
